title: Yo Soy Loco.
description:
Jackie announces some exciting news (don’t worry, she is not pregnant) drops some spicy marital advice and tackles religion (why?).

LISTEN UP! If you think my podcast is unhinged, you have no idea the crazy this Live Tour has in store for you. Be a loyal bitch and get your presale tickets at www.thebitchbible.com and use the promo code BBTOUR. There are a very limited number of VIP Meet & Greet packages available. General tickets go on sale Friday the 22nd at 10 AM.

Produced By Dear Media
